      "source": [
        "# MTCA-1 Stage 6: Full Council Execution\n",
        "\n",
        "**Study identifier:** MTCA-1\n",
        "**Stage:** 6 of 10 — Full execution of the council methodology\n",
        "**Inputs:** Stage 3 design (frozen at SHA `6380e711bbaed3af`) + Stage 5 pilot lessons\n",
        "**Outputs:** ~2,000 council responses (50 units × 8 frames × 5 models), one JSON file per response\n",
        "\n",
        "## Purpose\n",
        "\n",
        "Execute the full council protocol against the frozen Stage 3 design. Runs every (unit, frame, model) call in the execution plan, persisting each response to disk immediately. Designed for unattended overnight execution with resumability if Colab disconnects.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Lessons from pilot baked in\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Provider-specific token limits:** Gemini Flash gets 2500 max_tokens; other providers get 1500.\n",
        "- **Skip already-completed calls:** Each batch checks the response directory before calling, so a Colab disconnect costs only the in-flight batch.\n",
        "- **Batched checkpointing:** Execution proceeds in batches of 200 calls. After each batch, summary stats are saved and progress is reported.\n",
        "- **Resumability:** Re-running the notebook picks up where it left off — only un-executed calls are dispatched.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Expected execution\n",
        "\n",
        "- ~2,000 API calls\n",
        "- ~$6-10 total cost (pilot extrapolation projects $6.41)\n",
        "- ~3-6 hours wall-clock unattended\n",
        "- Batches: 10 batches of 200 calls each"
      ]
    },
